---

<MainLayout title="About CodeNHammer | UI Components for Contractors & Small Business Websites" description="Learn about CodeNHammer, created by freelance designers for freelance designers, offering specialized UI components and layouts for small businesses and contractors.">
    
    <Navigation4></Navigation4>
    <DocsLayout
        header="Introduction"
        description="Welcome to CodeNHammer! We're your one-stop-shop for a UI Component Library tailored just for freelance web designers who build websites for contractors and small businesses. CodeNHammer started because we got tired of doing the same tasks over and over when making websites. We wanted something that would make our lives easier, and we figured you might too.">

        <div class="p-4 space-y-2 max-w-3xl mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl text-neutral-900 font-bold">Our Goal</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-500 text-base leading-relaxed">We know that small businesses and contractors need quality websites that stand out without overloading your design process. CodeNHammer is here to help streamline your work by offering flexible, customizable components that cover all the essentials. Our goal is to save you time and give you the tools to deliver high-quality results for your clients with ease.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-4 space-y-2 max-w-3xl mb-4">
            <h3 class="text-2xl text-neutral-900 font-bold">Why Tailwind CSS and Alpine.js?</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-500 text-base leading-relaxed">So, why did we choose Tailwind CSS and Alpine.js for our tech stack? It’s pretty simple – speed. We wanted to make sure that not only could you develop your projects quickly, but that the end result would be super fast too.</p>
        </div>


