            <p class="text-neutral-500 text-base leading-relaxed">This utility-first framework lets you style components directly in HTML, so you can easily customize designs without wrangling complex CSS. It keeps your work flexible and efficient, letting you focus on creativity.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Line -->
        <div class="ml-12 h-16 w-px origin-top-left bg-blue-400 flex"></div>

